---
import Landing from '@/layout/Landing.astro';
---

<Landing 
    title="Cookie Policy" 
    description="Learn how Anyclazz uses cookies and similar technologies to improve your experience on our platform."
    keywords={['cookies', 'tracking', 'privacy', 'data collection']}
>
    <section class="px-4 pt-32 pb-20">
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center mb-16">
            <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-[var(--color-primary-700)] mb-3">Legal</p>
            <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-4">Cookie Policy</h1>
            <p class="text-lg text-neutral-500 max-w-[50ch]">How Anyclazz uses cookies and similar technologies on our platform.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="container mx-auto max-w-4xl">
        <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">

            <section class="mb-10">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-[var(--color-neutral-800)]">1. Introduction</h2>
                <p class="text-[var(--color-neutral-700)] mb-4">
                    This Cookie Policy explains how Anyclazz S.L. ("Anyclazz") uses cookies and similar technologies
                    when you access or use its platform.
                </p>
                <p class="text-[var(--color-neutral-700)]">
                    This Policy should be read together with the Privacy Policy.
                </p>
            </section>

            <section class="mb-10">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-[var(--color-neutral-800)]">2. What Are Cookies and Similar Technologies</h2>
                <p class="text-[var(--color-neutral-700)] mb-4">
                    Cookies are small text files stored on your device.
                </p>
                <p class="text-[var(--color-neutral-700)]">
                    Other tracking technologies include pixels, tags, and local storage used to collect and store information.
                </p>
            </section>

            <section class="mb-10">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-[var(--color-neutral-800)]">3. Categories of Cookies Used</h2>
                <p class="text-[var(--color-neutral-700)] mb-4">Anyclazz uses the following categories of cookies:</p>
                <ul class="list-decimal list-inside space-y-3 text-[var(--color-neutral-700)]">
                    <li><strong>Strictly Necessary Cookies:</strong> authentication, security, fraud prevention, payment processing</li>
                    <li><strong>Analytics Cookies:</strong> measure usage, traffic, and performance (e.g., Google Analytics)</li>
                    <li><strong>Marketing Cookies:</strong> track effectiveness of campaigns and deliver targeted advertising (e.g., Meta Pixel)</li>
                    <li><strong>Functional Cookies:</strong> remember preferences such as language or settings</li>
                </ul>
            </section>

            <section class="mb-10">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-[var(--color-neutral-800)]">4. Detailed Purpose of Cookies</h2>
                <p class="text-[var(--color-neutral-700)] mb-4">Cookies may be used to:</p>
                <ul class="list-decimal list-inside space-y-2 text-[var(--color-neutral-700)]">
                    <li>Authenticate users and maintain sessions</li>
                    <li>Prevent fraud and ensure platform security</li>
                    <li>Analyze user behavior and improve services</li>
                    <li>Personalize content and user experience</li>
                    <li>Deliver and measure advertising performance</li>
                </ul>
            </section>

            <section class="mb-10">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-[var(--color-neutral-800)]">5. Legal Basis (GDPR & ePrivacy)</h2>
                <p class="text-[var(--color-neutral-700)] mb-4">Under EU law:</p>
                <ul class="list-decimal list-inside space-y-2 text-[var(--color-neutral-700)]">
                    <li>Strictly necessary cookies are based on legitimate interest</li>
                    <li>All other cookies require prior user consent</li>
                </ul>
            </section>

            <section class="mb-10">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-[var(--color-neutral-800)]">6. US Privacy Considerations</h2>
                <p class="text-[var(--color-neutral-700)] mb-4">
                    For users in the United States, cookies and tracking technologies may be considered personal data
                    under applicable laws such as CCPA/CPRA.
                </p>
                <p class="text-[var(--color-neutral-700)]">
                    Anyclazz does not sell or share personal data for cross-context behavioral advertising.
                </p>
            </section>

            <section class="mb-10">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-[var(--color-neutral-800)]">7. Third-Party Cookies</h2>
                <p class="text-[var(--color-neutral-700)] mb-4">Third-party providers may place cookies on the platform:</p>
                <ul class="list-decimal list-inside space-y-2 text-[var(--color-neutral-700)]">
                    <li>Google (analytics services)</li>
                    <li>Meta (advertising and tracking)</li>
                    <li>Stripe (payment processing)</li>
                    <li>Other service providers as required</li>
                </ul>
            </section>

            <section class="mb-10">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-[var(--color-neutral-800)]">8. Cookie Consent Mechanism</h2>
                <p class="text-[var(--color-neutral-700)] mb-4">
                    When you first visit the platform, you will be presented with a consent banner that allows you to:
                </p>
                <ul class="list-decimal list-inside space-y-2 text-[var(--color-neutral-700)]">
                    <li>Accept all cookies</li>
                    <li>Reject non-essential cookies</li>
                    <li>Customize preferences by category</li>
                </ul>
            </section>

            <section class="mb-10">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-[var(--color-neutral-800)]">9. Consent Withdrawal</h2>
                <p class="text-[var(--color-neutral-700)]">
                    You can withdraw or modify your consent at any time through the cookie settings tool or browser settings.
                </p>
            </section>

            <section class="mb-10">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-[var(--color-neutral-800)]">10. Cookie Retention</h2>
                <p class="text-[var(--color-neutral-700)] mb-4">Cookies may be:</p>
                <ul class="list-decimal list-inside space-y-2 text-[var(--color-neutral-700)]">
                    <li>Session cookies (deleted when browser closes)</li>
                    <li>Persistent cookies (stored for defined periods depending on purpose)</li>
                </ul>
            </section>

            <section class="mb-10">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-[var(--color-neutral-800)]">11. Managing Cookies via Browser</h2>
                <p class="text-[var(--color-neutral-700)] mb-4">
                    You can manage cookies through your browser settings (Chrome, Safari, Firefox, Edge).
                </p>
                <p class="text-[var(--color-neutral-700)]">
                    Disabling cookies may impact functionality.
                </p>
            </section>

            <section class="mb-10">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-[var(--color-neutral-800)]">12. Data Sharing via Cookies</h2>
                <p class="text-[var(--color-neutral-700)]">
                    Information collected through cookies may be shared with service providers for analytics,
                    advertising, and technical functionality.
                </p>
            </section>

            <section class="mb-10">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-[var(--color-neutral-800)]">13. Updates to this Policy</h2>
                <p class="text-[var(--color-neutral-700)]">
                    We may update this Cookie Policy periodically. Users will be informed of significant changes.
                </p>
            </section>

            <section class="mb-10">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-[var(--color-neutral-800)]">14. Contact</h2>
                <p class="text-[var(--color-neutral-700)]">
                    For any questions: <a href="mailto:info@anyclazz.com" class="text-[var(--color-primary-600)] hover:underline">info@anyclazz.com</a>
                </p>
            </section>
        </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</Landing>
